"content": "<h2>Grandparents mentioned in Scripture</h2>\n<h3>Saul, the grandfather of Mephibosheth</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam9:7\">2SA 9:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam16:3\">2SA 16:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam19:26-2Sam19:28\">2SA 19:26–19:28</a></p>\n<h3>Maacah, the grandmother of Asa</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:9-1Kgs15:10\">1KI 15:9–15:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:13\">1KI 15:13</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr15:16\">2CH 15:16</a></p>\n<h3>Lois, the grandmother of Timothy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:5\">2TI 1:5</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Believers have a responsibility to support their grandparents</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:4\">1TI 5:4</a></strong></p>",
